Text: how do i install it / what is crake.. ? how do i find it

Install it as normal.
Step 1: Install "WebcamMax-7.1.3.2.MultiLanguage.Setup.exe"

Step 2: Make sure webcammax is not running, check bottom right corner tray to make sure it isnt there either.

Step 3: Go in to the "Crack" folder, highlight both the files "wcmhelper.dll" and "WebcamMax.exe" and copy them.

Step 4: go to "C:\Program Files\WebcamMax"

Step 5: Paste the two files you copied earlier, and REPLACE the original files.
